data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ***Seller is offering $5,000 towards closing costs with a full price offer*** Welcome to Your Dream Home in North Lakeland! Nestled in the highly sought-after Hunters Run Community, this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom pool home is a true gem. This residence offers the lifestyle you've been searching for. Enter through the welcoming foyer and discover the convenience of a split floor plan, designed to provide both privacy and ample communal space. Brand New Stainless Steel Appliances in the kitchen! The master suite is a serene retreat, boasting a spacious en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet, and direct access to the pool. One of the three additional bedrooms is located next to the master suite and is perfect for use as a bedroom or an office. Your private oasis awaits! Step out onto the spacious covered lanai (41 ftx10 ft) and envision the countless evenings spent relaxing or hosting outdoor dinners. The sparkling pool is perfect for cooling off on hot Florida days, and an outdoor shower adds a touch of luxury to your backyard experience. With smart exterior lighting, your evenings will always be well-lit. Enjoy added privacy with the new fence surrounding your property. A whole-house water softener ensures the best water quality for the home. Extended parking provides ample space for multiple vehicles. Plus, the recently painted exterior gives the home a fresh, inviting look. Hunters Run is known for its convenient location, close to shopping, dining, parks, and schools. Don't miss this opportunity to make this beautiful home your own! Schedule a showing today and experience the magic of this exceptional property for yourself.
